Experimental results for "A Shared-Memory Algorithm for Updating Tree-Based Properties of Large Dynamic Networks"¶

Edit the variables below to indicate which plots to generate, the algs list is a list of subdirectories with log files containing time, power, and energy measurements. The MST time, power, and energy totals include only the update values (not the building of the rooted tree, which is a one-time initial cost).
